{"tid":2033550,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵人開個eye catching既post， 關於每次遊行/活動既下半場","createTime":"2020-05-24T17:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T02:42:57.000Z","uid":110509,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"990fcfff690c7b0511d816ad62b1c3051aa49fce","tid":2033550,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T17:15:22.000Z","msg":"以下係point form<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 每次遊行完左都有好多人陣地戰，點解？因為無下半場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.離場返屋企，感覺好似一日咁就完左，搞左成日得個吉，無力感重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 1&amp;2導致手足傾向戀戰. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">*case by case，有d情況要留；有d情況要走，評論唔到*</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 下半場，其實係，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">twitter戰線</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.  遊行&amp;集會受眾係邊個（即係做俾咩人睇）<br />\n<br />\n香港人？ 黃定藍一早定晒，都有集氣作用既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府？ 只聽中共話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共？ 彩你都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.遊行&amp;集會 其實受眾係外國，即係係做俾外國睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. 所以，成功方程式係<br />\n遊行&gt;影靚相&gt;外媒報道，同時帶出主題（反惡法，反23條，臨時立法會etc）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8. 點解下半場係twitter戰線？（聰明既應該諗到）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9. 大量retweet &amp; like&amp; comment&gt; 爭取大量外國左膠關注&amp;支持&gt; 外國議員為呃票做野 （參考美國奶共民主黨爭住屌9中共）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.  最緊要係，對連登仔黎講，㩒2個制，其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11. 所以，成功方程式 之 簡單修定版：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遊行集會（上半場）&gt; 靚相&gt; 外媒頭版&gt; twitter（下半場）&gt;  外國圍屌&amp;圍堵中共 &gt;支爆&gt; 支爆爆&gt;支爆爆爆</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n12. 哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n13. 哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n14. 哈哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n15. 記得每次遊行集會完左做咩未？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係下半場開始！準備twitter 做建盤戰士喇</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n16. 認真，前線手足好憎俾政黨消費光環， 但絕對唔介意各位係國際上消費佢地光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請你地係國際層面上盡情消費手足光環，直到香港重光！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs1. 鬼佬好懶，歐洲人中午4至5點先起身，美國人夜晚8點9點先起身<br />\n<br />\n所以入黑差唔多返屋企，開始打好下半場去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs2. 請睇pin，twitter 戰線 簡易bot"},{"pid":"d3b7a377aee52f67edaab16a600405fe5e896f2d","tid":2033550,"uid":110509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"有無手足幫我搵個twitter bot 俾我pin<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85d3379f6904d9a6e39ac1b64d440ce64c4a60a","tid":2033550,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"12-14想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6fefd559dab68b803406e6d935ad6a2f8ec3b1","tid":2033550,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85d3379f6904d9a6e39ac1b64d440ce64c4a60a","tid":2033550,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T17:17:10.000Z",